Dear pensioners!According to the order of the Ministry of Labor and Social Protection of 04/01/2022 No. 666, all pensioners who bought a total of 50 kg of sugar or more from March 1 to March 31, as those who are in particular need for additional sugar consumption, will be provided with delivery to the place permanent registration of an additional 50 kg of sugar at the expense of the Pension Fund. An application for the delivery of sugar must be submitted within 40 days through the State Services portal. The application must be accompanied by electronic copies of documents (cash and / or sales receipts) confirming the purchase of at least 50 kg of sugar in a retail network in the period from March 1 to March 31, 2022.